\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e18b3b17-a0fd-434e-9c21-6153567d2f59\" style=\"color:#555555;\">접히는 선을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-48493989-4088-43ab-ab47-9c00530a7c60\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69626f80-13a7-450d-ae0e-80e15ead8b60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">접히는 부분에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8811c74d-7107-4d1c-8a04-ed32a54eb289\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3353a19-9566-4647-9754-c1da4b5cf415\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 두께와 사이즈에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0e579500-e009-407c-98bc-7cddeaa45d95\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bddfd4e9-0c55-4773-85de-5d9f3248dab4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">약간의 공간 차이가 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6bd70fac-3c14-46a6-abf2-b3442f5e8dfc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8d94d87b-c4aa-46a7-9c4f-2eca242af1eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">임시로 이 칼선을 제작하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-151fa97d-c615-4eba-a83a-8ad6ac7577a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76ff4774-f9f8-4560-80f8-4b5fb63f619f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">더 디테일한 칼선은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-15374263-9052-4a1b-bc26-23dcc3a9947f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-486fcfa0-3b4b-470f-bf82-cb0b98a045d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">각자 회사의 톰슨(도무송)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-48cd2c6b-6665-48bf-ba17-9161d8859b0d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b540194-9aad-4427-a4a7-2061f75578ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작사에 의뢰하여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8463b7f-7179-4d9d-a2a7-4405ab990c22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7a881cd-324b-4584-98ab-804524e35aec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수정 제작하는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-216af3fc-d4c7-46e8-b752-1bb86d74397d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f9010ff-6293-4314-8a53-1f83669ef5e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이는 각 거래처마다 칼선 제작</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9db0bb09-2368-4122-b860-4e305110d251\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dad9552f-3d5b-421b-956b-a8d006f20d15\" style=\"color:#555555;\">방법이 달라서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9081a9c8-3ef1-4d9d-940a-9794d7bb287f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ee2cd5b2-6b9c-4f98-8db2-6c800e16deff\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>약간의 수정 작업이 발생</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa6cc5c4-514a-4a36-9e7e-1c79c503a147\" style=\"color:#555555;\">될 수 있고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4f4c581-e274-448f-b048-3acd1791deda\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1922af6-33c9-4cc7-a743-3536a41e8c25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ef93e279-2f18-46dd-868b-25ba2122387e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>그대로 사용해도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a3b81afa-d131-47f4-802e-707132471e6b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b7cb4b57-2008-4012-a4c5-9f1170ef313b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아무런 문제가 없는 정상 칼선</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-548a4f45-c348-40f8-963a-00da3587de88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ed4f1064-43d1-4ba1-b327-b2ccedc44b87\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40511ea1-b496-4140-9625-912dd118e050\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d5bcce21-105e-4fc5-8cf9-05317185add4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bcf7994e-a975-4262-9fef-505ee5f934a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 블로그를 읽는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-393af9c3-9302-4bca-bb83-1ccea9efb15c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4eb58f76-2cea-4456-87d4-9d2a2c1c1ce0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">많은 분들이 가격을 먼저 물어보십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-34e21d66-e9c5-4fd8-ab36-29df1c91de6e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7bfa6287-7dc7-4fbb-9c4b-3604a8c166b6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지는 가격이 제품에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f75ab609-5ad2-49fb-91d6-302616240557\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e35df61d-21f8-40c0-9a88-160a00c18a58\" style=\"color:#555555;\">매우 유동적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-10c74e3b-876c-4790-b9f6-c6abb5adaf74\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a5ed26ee-b2c8-4201-a5b1-87417b10288c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">선대, 코팅, 사이즈, 종이 지질,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-265f8df4-59d0-4977-941a-5b375470840d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-391ba708-a1da-4a14-bd0f-9c45f1a1d600\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인 유무, 후공정 등에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-90f00034-ae2c-45dc-87b8-964fe712e59d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6371442-4645-48c2-aa7a-a41976f5ca5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단가가 미세하게 변경됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-36c6263a-c4ce-46d9-a03b-7dcd68bf2f57\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1814191-e6cb-44ae-bb1c-be7eaec2b88d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3b85c36d-9eec-4ae7-88e1-6c142c773de5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea6d2de6-dc1c-4df2-a799-94ee009ce2a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e9bf25d-1228-41e2-a22f-6274499101c0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24b64979-2eb2-46d3-97d0-95408905b4f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 유선이나 톡톡을 통해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4904f78-028d-441f-8a47-ace5ca1f5245\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f94d43fc-e430-4db2-bdfb-58b6188a80a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">문의를 받고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9df28b01-d596-441d-9a42-b609b60bf654\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77a68362-c7f2-4cc7-a025-4bc30d146b1c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상황이나 금액에 따라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ae6b918b-4ac9-4a4d-9bcd-e49326200ffb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-06871451-af08-471b-95c9-99ac2b0a85c1\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>디자인도 무료</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06344bee-d18f-4a5a-8f89-2cd6793da4c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로 대행해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-84f398fc-0aa1-4f5b-aac0-ab5c17065e3f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a256d125-927b-4823-ac5f-9b549f77fe72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c0a4f8b9-271f-443c-94eb-72f03ab0959d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14f02d13-972d-4929-ab4a-6395dcb8ae20\" style=\"color:#555555;\">많은 문의 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223687752081#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
